  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for xen",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for xen fixes the following issues:\n\n- bsc#1177409 - VUL-0: CVE-2020-27673: xen: x86 PV guest INVLPG-like flushes may leave stale TLB entries (XSA-286)\n- bsc#1177412 - VUL-0: CVE-2020-27672: xen: Race condition in Xen mapping code (XSA-345)\n- bsc#1177413 - VUL-0: CVE-2020-27671: xen: undue deferral of IOMMU TLB flushes (XSA-346)\n- bsc#1177414 - VUL-0: CVE-2020-27670: xen: unsafe AMD IOMMU page table updates (XSA-347)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
